{"tid":1448982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T21:25:32.000Z","uid":36657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9ca020a4c27fd30db0c38d7ddd5b094c28bcfa","tid":1448982,"uid":36657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=2ba4a4d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f09f499a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"9113f9ffcbf06658d8f753885716f70ab6b99faf","tid":1448982,"uid":36657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bafb7d2d928280d2537c70783f704ea906c1c3c0","tid":1448982,"uid":9192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b60e8d8a2da58f83dce78a286c50c114c32268ec","tid":1448982,"uid":36657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05559dfd1ef37bac5ccc645b71d75cbdd78e4c25","tid":1448982,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:25:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}